  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of ALX-0600 in Subjects With Active Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study of the Safety and Efficacy of ALX-0600 in Subjects With Moderately Active Crohn's Disease</official_title>
