  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine whether an investigational compound, ALX-0600, is
      safe and effective in treating Crohn's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study is twelve weeks in duration and there are eight weeks of once-daily injections into
      your abdomen or thigh. There are a total of six visits.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
